proxy.name: proxy
proxy.organization: National Laboratory for Applied Network Research
proxy.contactinfo: Glenn Chisholm Postal: National Centre for Atmospheric Research (NCAR) Room 36, SCD PO Box 3000 Boulder, Colorado 80307 US Tel: +1 303 497 1289 Fax: +1 303 497 1818 E-mail: glenn@ircache.net
proxy.description: Proxy MIB defined for the generic management of proxy devices. See http://www.ircache.net/Cache/cache-snmp/.

proxyMemUsage.name: proxyMemUsage
proxyMemUsage.description: The memory in use by the proxy independant of the support processes on the system running the proxy

proxyStorage.name: proxyStorage
proxyStorage.description: The quantity of storage in use by the proxy in KB. This value can be zero if there is no caching occuring.

proxyCpuUsage.name: proxyCpuUsage
proxyCpuUsage.description: The amount of CPU consumed over the life of the process in seconds.

proxyUpTime.name: proxyUpTime
proxyUpTime.description: The amount of time the proxy has been running, in TimeTicks.

proxyAdmin.name: proxyAdmin
proxyAdmin.description: The contact responsible for the administration of the proxy. Usually a name and email address.

proxyCpuLoad.name: proxyCpuLoad
proxyCpuLoad.description: The current percentage of the CPU being consumed by the proxy proccess at this time.

proxyNumObjects.name: proxyNumObjects
proxyNumObjects.description: The number of objects currently held by the proxy.

proxyClientHttpRequests.name: proxyClientHttpRequests
proxyClientHttpRequests.description: The number of HTTP requests recieved from clients.

proxyClientHttpHits.name: proxyClientHttpHits
proxyClientHttpHits.description: The number of HTTP hits that the proxy clients have produced.

proxyClientHttpErrors.name: proxyClientHttpErrors
proxyClientHttpErrors.description: The number of HTTP errors caused by client connections.

proxyClientHttpInKbs.name: proxyClientHttpInKbs
proxyClientHttpInKbs.description: The number of kilobits recieved from the clients by the proxy.

proxyClientHttpOutKbs.name: proxyClientHttpOutKbs
proxyClientHttpOutKbs.description: The number of kilobits delivered to clients from the proxy.

proxyServerHttpRequests.name: proxyServerHttpRequests
proxyServerHttpRequests.description: The number of HTTP requests that the proxy has issued.

proxyServerHttpErrors.name: proxyServerHttpErrors
proxyServerHttpErrors.description: The number of HTTP errors while fetching objects.

proxyServerHttpInKbs.name: proxyServerHttpInKbs
proxyServerHttpInKbs.description: The number of Kbs recieved by the proxy from remote servers.

proxyServerHttpOutKbs.name: proxyServerHttpOutKbs
proxyServerHttpOutKbs.description: The number of kbs transmitted by the proxy to remote servers.

proxyMedianSvcTable.name: proxyMedianSvcTable
proxyMedianSvcTable.description: The table of median statistics serviced by the proxy indexed by the median time.

proxyMedianTime.name: proxyMedianTime
proxyMedianTime.description: The median time used to index the table proxyMedianSvcTable.

proxyHTTPAllSvcTime.name: proxyHTTPAllSvcTime
proxyHTTPAllSvcTime.description: The service time for all HTTP requests.

proxyHTTPMissSvcTime.name: proxyHTTPMissSvcTime
proxyHTTPMissSvcTime.description: The service time for all HTTP misses.

proxyHTTPHitSvcTime.name: proxyHTTPHitSvcTime
proxyHTTPHitSvcTime.description: The service time for all HTTP hits.

proxyHTTPNhSvcTime.name: proxyHTTPNhSvcTime
proxyHTTPNhSvcTime.description: The service time for all HTTP near hits.
